title: [Chocolate Brown Conical Tent]
description: Draped with beige felt, the interior of the tent is deceptively large.  A brass-banded wooden chest rests at the foot of a large wooden cot draped with a plum-hued comforter that dominates the center of the room.  The perimeter is dotted with a series of thick white candles, their wide wooden bases carved with a spiral of blossoms.
